SubjectOrder Designating the Honourable Patricia A. Hajdu to Co-ordinate Policy with respect to the Status of Women and Administer Related Programs
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2015-1249 of November 4, 2015; and (2) designating the Hon. PATRICIA A. HAJDU, a member of the Queen’s Privy Council for Canada, to co-ordinate policy with respect to the status of women and administer related programs.
